<section class="block-section story">
  <span class="section-tag">📖 Story</span>
  <h2>Why this block matters</h2>
  <p class="sub">The Communication performance. Your work goes public.</p>
  <p>This is the unit's Communication performance, and it is the upgrade over a peer-only panel: you present your neighbourhood redesign as a real public activity at the school's environmental showcase, framed for a real municipal audience (the Greater Chennai Corporation, the CMDA, or your ward office). The live activity teaches other students the choice your neighbourhood faces, and your shareable artifact carries the same message to a wider audience with appropriate consent. The bar is not a polished slogan. It is whether your audience can see both what your plan achieves and what it costs.</p>
  <p class="sub" style="color: var(--muted);">Full block content lands in the Unit 6 deep build. Whether the unit runs during the school's environmental showcase week is an open scheduling decision, so this page stays date-free.</p>
</section>

